    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Object genre including a wide variety of items used in a domestic environment, excluding large furniture. Can include draperies, rugs, decorative items, small furnishings, wallcoverings, and many other types of things, both decorative and functional.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
